Amazing place
A real revelation: you realize, afer seeing this, how evoluated was the Cham culture and how the two religion, Buddhism and Hindu clashed then blended.
There is a lot of simbolistic involved and, if you are familiar with or at least have a reading interest in the Hindu deities and stories, it really gets your attention.
A small gem all in all; do not miss it under any circumstances while in Da Nang.
Interestion souvenir shop also, with some books in English and French but also a lot of stone reproductions.
